{"tid":1391074,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國參議員帕特圖米：我支持《香港人權與民主法案》以重申美國與為自由奮鬥的港人站在一起。","createTime":"2019-07-31T10:19:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T10:53:12.000Z","uid":70063,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7513c6b4e809e5c329d25e8e09e574ce3399247e","tid":1391074,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"中國獨裁主義威脅香港人的言論自由、公平審訊和代表制政府的權利。我支持《香港人權與民主法案》以重申美國與為自由奮鬥的港人站在一起。<br />\n<br />\nChinese authoritarianism threatens Hong Kongers' rights to free speech, a fair trial, &amp; representative government. I'm backing @marcorubio's bipartisan bill reaffirming that the U.S. stands with Hong Kongers in their struggle for freedom. <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2yzUxYF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2yzUxYF&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=63e056c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2yzUxYF</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenToomey/status/1156205169207578624\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenToomey%2Fstatus%2F1156205169207578624&d=UHNfIMcGe5kTnAHmubppFnwvfzOYOHHotQSumXQzHeA%3D&h=cadc14cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSenToomey%2Fstatus%2F1156205169207578624&h=10edb468\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/SenToomey/status/1156205169207578624</a>"},{"pid":"2c82753a8efb0ee1e7ba7df369acc9f8946a6be8","tid":1391074,"uid":6604,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"快啲通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00db180a725795baec7b7752a68d093fe54a7c1","tid":1391074,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:22:01.000Z","msg":"【暗黑經濟學】發夢原則<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1390973\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1390973</a>"},{"pid":"a7ee256fcabffed515ca41ebefb16701a011a3a6","tid":1391074,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T10:53:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"}]}